The paper focuses on quality assurance technologies for big data applications, which involves software engineering (cs.SE) and database systems (cs.DB) to handle the large volume, velocity, and variety of data. The paper also discusses various techniques such as analysis, verification, and testing, which are commonly used in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and distributed computing (cs.DC). Additionally, the paper touches upon fault tolerance and failure prediction, which are relevant to computer security (cs.CR).
